  "description": "This individual is an undead figure preserved by brine exposure, bearing brown skin that has hardened into a salt-cured, fissured texture. Gray eyes sit deep beneath heavy, collapsed lids, and gray hair grows in sparse, brittle strands across a shrunken scalp. The mouthline is set in a permanent retraction that exposes darkened teeth, while the hands remain permanently warped into grasping hooks by long desiccation. The frame is narrow and ropey, with joints fixed in angles that reflect years of cramped immobility in wet stone hollows.",
